# Business / customer-confidential docs — local only, never push.
# Code is open for reference; business logic, post-demo briefs, customer-facing
# scripts are NOT to be committed (đạo đức kinh doanh, kể cả khi chưa kí NDA).
# Pre-commit hook also blocks these — see scripts/git-hooks/pre-commit.
# Override (audited exception): SKIP_BUSINESS_DOC_GUARD=1 git commit ...
docs/backend-business-logic-*.md
docs/*business-logic*.md
docs/post-demo-pivot-brief.md
docs/*pivot-brief*.md
docs/demo-prototype-script.md
docs/*demo-script*.md
docs/customer-*.md
docs/*-customer-*.md
